{
  "stem": "27335.7",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That it takes all this, and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we-- we had to disarm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We have to, if possible, silently disarm.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Silent killing. dagger, and so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because you can't do shooting, going around at the-- at the bridge heads and so on, to get rid of the German-- German guard.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then find what you call-- And that's-- and it is my job, where and how to cut the-- cut the wires, to be saved, not to explode it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But to neutralize it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, not-- not at this moment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the very evening that I was taken into the [NON-ENGLISH] house-- into the [NON-ENGLISH] house, the second floor was an exclusive quarter for the son of the-- of the family, [NON-ENGLISH] Jr.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a-- he was a-- he-- he was a lawyer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when-- when I was in-- I-- I was introduced, we shook hand with [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a Jewish fellow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a friend of-- a friend of [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he slept upstairs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we slept in the adjoining-- adjoining-- the rooms upstairs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because he said what-- and no family you have-- what you call them-- could-- could-- it was like-- like a neighbor-- neighbor's house.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, it was-- it was a villa, you see?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they build it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They could afford it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so-- Yes?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But [NON-ENGLISH] was-- his friend and-- but mind you, he spent almost six months in the attic.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [NON-ENGLISH] used to steal from the kitchen. it was literally food, and take him up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Finally, after months, his mother caught him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Except the maid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She knows because she had to go-- go up there when they washed the-- that's where they hung their laundry and so on.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But she kept quiet.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
